  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>A buffet breakfast to start the day is available from 7.30 – 9.30am. This includes hot drinks, juices, pastries, breads, assortment or jams and spreads, fresh fruit and cereals. There’s also a warm savoury buffet of eggs, bacon, sausages etc and cheeses.</p>
<p>Three course buffet evening meal, with wine included, is served from 7 – 8.30pm. There are different themes to the buffet, with regional, international dishes and show cooking. One Savoyard raclette meal is included each week, please pre-book this in resort.</p>
<p>Early meal times for children are available during school holidays, this will be 6.45pm.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>0</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Diva is located right in the resort centre of Val Claret in <a data-udi="umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565" href="/{localLink:umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565}" title="Tignes">Tignes</a>. With a short walk to the ski lifts and the Grand Motte funicular its perfect to get out onto the slopes and in this amazing ski area each day. The terrace and bar area is the perfect place to come back to after the slopes, and treat yourself to that well deserved drink or a game of pool. Each evening there's a live band or piano entertainment to enjoy. </p>
<p>The steam room and sauna is great for relaxing the muscles after a day on the slopes. There's also the free day care services for 3 - 10 year olds too.</p>
<p>Start your day with the large buffet breakfast, perfectly fuelled for the slopes. Then go on to treat yourself in the evenings with the buffet dinner or even with a raclette night.</p>]]></description>
