  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p>All bedrooms have a bath with shower head attached and WC.</p>
<p><strong>Classic twin rooms</strong> sleep up to 2 people, are 16-19m<sup>2 </sup>and have a twin bed.</p>
<p><strong>Classic family rooms</strong> can sleep up to 4 people and are 20-25m<sup>2</sup>. Main bed can be twin or double (please specify at time of booking) and extra beds are either a trundle bed or bunk beds.</p>
<p><strong>Classic double rooms</strong> sleep up to 2 people and are 21m<sup>2</sup>. This room has a double bed and a balcony.</p>
<p>Beds made on arrival and daily housekeeping included.</p>
<p><strong>Room facilities </strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Hairdryer </li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
